               <p>(The case was opened by Mr. Knapp.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17930911-93-person1051">
                  WILLIAM
                   FRAMPTON
               <interp inst="t17930911-93-person1051" type="surname" value="FRAMPTON"></interp>
